<h2>3. Window Function - ROW_NUMBER()</h2>
<h3>Query</h3>
<pre><code class="language-sql">SELECT emp_id,
       emp_name,
       salary,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY salary DESC) AS row_no
FROM Employee;
</code></pre>
