<h2>5. CASE WHEN</h2>
<h3>Query</h3>
<pre><code class="language-sql">SELECT emp_name,
       salary,
       CASE
           WHEN salary &gt;= 80000 THEN 'High Salary'
           WHEN salary &gt;= 60000 THEN 'Medium Salary'
           ELSE 'Low Salary'
       END AS Salary_Category
FROM Employee;
</code></pre>
